    "created_at": "2015-10-27T02:26:41Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-10-27T02:26:41Z",
    "body": "There is no data type in JavaScript can represent a native handle, we can probably add an API to return a `v8::External` or `node::Buffer` which contains an external pointer to the handle of native window, and then users can receive the handle by writing a native module.\n"
