    "updated_at": "2016-01-06T12:32:35Z",
    "body": "Unsigend integer would not suffice as explained here https://github.com/atom/electron/pull/3256#issuecomment-152005215.\nStroring the pointer in a buffer is a pattern already being used in the pull request mentioned above.\nI actually started working on the pull request which should have been simple, but encountered unexpected problems.\nI had some difficulties finding time to keep working on it, but I will soon.\n@skreborn You are more then welcome to help with it if you'd like :smile: \n"
