    "body": "@omrilitov Okay, fair point about the inability to guarantee V8's inner workings, so a `Buffer` might just be the better choice. I would love to help out, although right now I have no idea how to do that.\n\nAlso, doesn't `GetAcceleratedWidget` work on all platforms? If not, why not? Haven't had the time to check out the code regarding this. The type of value it returns (`AcceleratedWidget`) is defined for most (if not all) supported platforms.\n"
